
The pro in this directory is mainly used to calculate the results. It contains many pros for calculating grid data (daily, monthly)

(1). daily_grid_LST : change MODIS LST resolution to 0.5*0.5 degree

(2). daily_grid_LST_AOD : change MODIS LST resolution to 0.5*0.5 degree under the condition of AOD.
(a), plot_LST_grid_daily_AODl5_v1.pro : AOD>0.5
(b), plot_LST_grid_daily_AODs2_v1.pro : AOD<0.2
(c), plot_LST_grid_daily_AODs5_v1.pro : AOD<0.5
(d), select_data_fl.pro : select the same time(the same file) between MODIS LST products and MODIS AOD products
(e), process_day.pro : read the time from LST, AOD, and fire products

(3), daily_grid_LST_fire_AOD : change MODIS LST resolution to 0.5*0.5 degree under the condition of AOD and with fire pixel.
(a), plot_LST_grid_daily_fire_AODl5_v1.pro : AOD>0.5
(b), plot_LST_grid_daily_fire_AODs2_v1.pro : AOD<0.2
(c), plot_LST_grid_daily_fire_AODs5_v1.pro : AOD<0.5

(4), daily_grid_LST_fire_no : change MODIS LST resolution to 0.5*0.5 degree under the condition of without fire pixel
(a), plot_LST_grid_daily_fire_v1.pro : main code
(b), select_data_fl.pro : select the LST and fire produts with the same time


